---
title: Home
layout: main
pagination:
  data: collections.post
  size: 10
  alias: posts
  reverse: true
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Home
  order: 1
---

<p class="lead">I don't Cosplay, but my daughter does and I let her use my workshop to work on her projects. The posts here highlight the tools and equipment I provide her to use with her projects.</p>

{% for post in posts reversed %}
  <p>
    <a href="{{post.url}}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>, posted {{ post.date | niceDate }}<br/>
    {% excerpt post %}
  </p>
{% endfor %}

<p>
  {% if pagination.href.previous %}
    <a href=" {{ pagination.href.previous }}">Previous</a>
  {% else %}
    Previous
  {% endif %}
  /
  {% if pagination.href.next %}
    <a href=" {{ pagination.href.next }}">Next</a>
  {% else %}
    Next
  {% endif %}
</p>